import requests,re
base='https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/e/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde.cxg/'
jsurl=base+'static/main-c01f72fa4f9cb0261568.js'
js=requests.get(jsurl, timeout=10).text
print('len', len(js))
for pat in ['api.cellxgene', 'api.cellxgene.cziscience.com', 'cellxgene.cziscience.com/api', '/api/','datasets','annotations','cell_type','tissue','schema']:
    print(pat, js.find(pat))
# find probable API base variable
m=re.search(r'https://api\.cellxgene\.cziscience\.com[^"\']*', js)
print('first api url match', m.group(0) if m else None)
# find all occurrences of api.cellxgene
indices=[m.start() for m in re.finditer('api.cellxgene', js)]
print('api.cellxgene occurrences', len(indices))
if indices:
    idx=indices[0]
    print(js[idx-80:idx+200])
# find endpoints patterns like "/api/v0.2/" etc
endpts=set(re.findall(r'/api/v\d+\.\d+[^"\']*', js))
print('some endpoints', list(endpts)[:20])
